My husband and I love this unusual take on chicken salad and it has become a summer stand-by for us. The only thing I change in the recipe is to use toasted pine nuts and I brine the chicken BRIEFLY instead of salting it immediately before cooking. I make extra tarragon dressing and pesto and refrigerate it until I need it.

