The recipe came out just as good as it looked on the cover of Bon Appetit. I added one clove of garlic to the pesto instead of the shallot and also made double the amount of pesto. I used the extra to brush on the chicken before grilling. My husband and I both loved this recipe and are looking forward to the leftovers tonight.